.Language=English,English
.Options CtrlStartPosChar=^<wrap>

@Contents
$^#Memo#
 #The following keys may be used:#
     #Esc#            Exit
     #Alt+0 - Alt+9#  Switch to another memo
     #Mouse click on indicator#  Switch to another memo
     #Shift+F2#       Save as... (the path may be changed)
     #Shift+F6#       Rename the current memo (no path change)

 #Note:#
   Exiting and switching between memos automatically save the current memo
   if it was modified.
